Defaults to the most universal implementation in SIMDJSON_IMPLEMENTATION (in the order fallback;westmere;haswell;icelake;arm64;ppc64) if specified; otherwise, by default the compiler will pick the best implementation that can always be selected given the compiler flags.

properties.name: HELPSTRING
